Package Controller.Phases.SubPhases

Class PlaySetupPhase

java.lang.Object
Controller.Phases.Phase
Controller.Phases.PlayGamePhase
Controller.Phases.SubPhases.PlaySetupPhase
public class PlaySetupPhase
extends PlayGamePhase
Represents the setup phase in the game. In this phase, players load a map, configure game players, and assign countries. Once all players and countries are assigned, the phase transitions to the issue order phase. This phase also handles some invalid commands and messages.
